where the water hyacinth couldn't grow,

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:55.000
the sand is flowing in these canals.

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:59.000
The bonus is that you can find wildlife around it.

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:02.000
(Laughter)

