00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:56.000
collects rainwater drops

00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:01.000
and deposit in the rooms.

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:04.000
But apart from this system,

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:10.000
