00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:40.000
It squeeze the moisture

00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:42.000
hidden in the sand.

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:46.000
And they have dubbed this water as the third one called [unclear].

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:51.000
